@startuml TheAllNewBinance_Overview
title TheAllNewBinance - Module Overview

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

[client] as clientModule
[core] as coreModule
[server] as serverModule
database "MySQL" as mysql

clientModule --> coreModule : shared models/contracts
serverModule --> coreModule : implements interfaces
serverModule --> mysql : JDBC persistence
clientModule ..> serverModule : target runtime integration\n(current client still uses placeholders)

note right of clientModule
  JavaFX UI module
  - scene/page/component structure
  - hot reload in dev mode
  - data currently mocked
end note

note right of coreModule
  Shared layer
  - entities
  - DTOs
  - DAO interfaces
  - service interfaces
  - protocol
  - utils
end note

note right of serverModule
  Backend layer
  - WebSocket entrypoint
  - request dispatcher
  - controllers
  - services
  - DAO implementations
end note

@enduml
